                <ns0:body>
                    <ns0:div type="edition" subtype="interpretive" xml:space="preserve" />
                     <ns0:div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="A">
                                            <ns0:ab>                            
                            <ns0:lb n="1" />Quan(n)o sancta <ns0:seg type="phoneme" subtype="j_initial">I</ns0:seg>uliana co(m)matteio coll<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> diavol<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> et
                            <ns0:lb n="2" />sì·ll<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> ven<ns0:seg type="grapheme" corresp="/ts/">ç</ns0:seg>e che ll<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> legone colla oratione.
                            <ns0:lb n="3" />Questa <ns0:m type="essere" subtype="pres3ps">ene</ns0:m> la cappella <ns0:m type="possessivo" subtype="3ps_fm">sova</ns0:m>.						
                                            </ns0:ab></ns0:div>
                         <ns0:div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="B">
                         <ns0:ab>
                            <ns0:lb n="1" />Quan(n)o sanct<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> Antoni<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> de Paduva liberone
                            <ns0:lb n="2" />una donna che aveva la can(n)a grossa
                            <ns0:lb n="3" />che <ns0:w>mo</ns0:w> è sana per gratia de Dio.						
                             </ns0:ab>
                         </ns0:div>
                             <ns0:div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="C">
                                 <ns0:ab>
                            Hoc opus fecit fi&lt;e&gt;ri Amicus de Stabilibus cano(ni)c(u)s Reatino(rum) huius cappelle cappellan(us) p(er) sua devotione et p(ro) a(n)i(m)a sua et suo(rum) defunto(rum) ac et(iam) benefacto(rum) p(re)dice cappelle sub an[no] D(omi)ni 1489 die 6 iulii
                        </ns0:ab>
                    </ns0:div>
                    <ns0:div type="edition" subtype="diplomatic" xml:space="preserve">
                        <ns0:div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="A">
                                            <ns0:ab>                            
                            <ns0:lb n="1" />Quan(n)o sancta Iuliana co(m)matteio coll<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> diavol<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> et
                            <ns0:lb n="2" />sì·ll<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> ven<ns0:seg type="grapheme" corresp="/ts/">ç</ns0:seg>e che ll<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> legone colla oratione.
                            <ns0:lb n="3" />Questa <ns0:m type="essere" subtype="pres3ps">ene</ns0:m> la cappella <ns0:m type="possessivo" subtype="3ps_fm">sova</ns0:m>.						
                                            </ns0:ab></ns0:div>
                         <ns0:div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="B">
                         <ns0:ab>
                            <ns0:lb n="1" />Quan(n)o sanct<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> Antoni<ns0:m type="desinence" subtype="ms_sing">u</ns0:m> de Paduva liberone
                            <ns0:lb n="2" />una donna che aveva la can(n)a grossa
                            <ns0:lb n="3" />che <ns0:w>mo</ns0:w> è sana per gratia de Dio.						
                             </ns0:ab>
                         </ns0:div>
                             <ns0:div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="C">
                                 <ns0:ab>
                            Hoc opus fecit fi&lt;e&gt;ri Amicus de Stabilibus cano(ni)c(u)s Reatino(rum) huius cappelle cappellan(us) p(er) sua devotione et p(ro) a(n)i(m)a sua et suo(rum) defunto(rum) ac et(iam) benefacto(rum) p(re)dice cappelle sub an[no] D(omi)ni 1489 die 6 iulii
                        </ns0:ab>
